pts from several of her works. Copub: Henry Art Gallery, University of Washington  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / General.2bisacsh1 aDietz, Steve, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFox, Howard N., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGagnon, Jean, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHeld, Robin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHershman, Lynn, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHershman, Lynn, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aJames, David E., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJones, Amelia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKinder, Marsha, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKurtz, Glenn, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRich, B. Ruby, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSolomon-Godeau, Abigail, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTromble, Meredith, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTromble, Meredith, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z978311069042240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052093744440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520937444423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520937444/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles